Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.00,0:01:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十九話\N史上最強的宿敵\N襲擊而來的無情之牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.55,0:01:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燒好像退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.76,0:02:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再拿水來換
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.01,0:02:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禰彥  左之助現在怎麼樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經退燒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.85,0:02:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要靜養就應該沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎  這樣我就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.12,0:02:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是什麼人對左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.69,0:02:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下這麼狠毒的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.14,0:02:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤究竟為何不直接找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.51,0:02:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而要如此對待左之助呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.28,0:02:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道他有什麼目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.62,0:03:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你久等了  請慢用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.89,0:03:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.09,0:03:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.66,0:03:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中午只吃一碗麵太少了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喜歡中午吃麵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.74,0:03:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你以後叫我藤田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是赤末先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.75,0:03:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找我有何貴幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.28,0:03:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.71,0:03:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,涉海老闆要我來看看你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.09,0:03:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件工作是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.46,0:03:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是一聽到你的名氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.06,0:03:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果就變成讓你來干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.23,0:03:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我看你不怎麼順眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.73,0:03:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽好  你行的話就快點解決掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.97,0:03:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼要吩咐的話\N就盡快說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.60,0:03:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,免得到時候我被人放冷劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於你的不滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.55,0:04:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我感到失敬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.68,0:04:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就讓我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.29,0:04:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起聯手來打擊敵人吧\N怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.85,0:04:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼  你要我怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.99,0:04:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.83,0:04:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次我去神谷道場時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.47,0:04:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故意的留下了一些線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.90,0:04:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在他應該發現我的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.21,0:04:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但還不知道我的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.74,0:04:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你幫我把這封信帶去給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把他引出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.28,0:04:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要我去引他出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.85,0:04:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你能把他殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.19,0:04:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就和你平分酬勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.62,0:04:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.76,0:04:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡  你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.10,0:04:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心 向來是你的頭號大敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.60,0:05:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如此輕易的讓我來解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.54,0:05:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我曾對涉海說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村劍心是我的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.87,0:05:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但事實上他在我眼中已微不足道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.88,0:05:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.14,0:05:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我最大的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.05,0:05:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是好好的過完我的下半輩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.82,0:05:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與其冒險換取高額賞金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如可以確確實實的領到花用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.92,0:05:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是這樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.66,0:05:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我並不想幫你做這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衝你這句話我就幫你一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.87,0:05:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但僅此一次  下不為例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.14,0:05:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這只井底之蛙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.28,0:05:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我根本不把你放在眼中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.77,0:06:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰要你去買豆腐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.08,0:06:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起  禰彥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.44,0:06:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有點事要出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能會晚點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.35,0:06:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚上記得把門窗關好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.15,0:06:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊  那我不是要去買豆腐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.42,0:06:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  我又不是沒事做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.77,0:06:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤  你終於要出現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.94,0:06:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要看你究竟在玩什麼把戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.94,0:07:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是緋村劍心  好快的身手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.61,0:07:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.68,0:07:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤末有人  來取你的性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.92,0:07:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心有事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.55,0:07:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他說要晚點回來\N喏豆腐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.69,0:07:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他還有沒有說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.66,0:07:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊  他還看了一封信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.20,0:07:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.00,0:07:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了  是情書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是女孩子寫給他的情書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.07,0:07:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難怪劍心什麼也不說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.04,0:07:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好真的會很晚才回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂  人家好不容易買來的豆腐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差點被你摔壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助現在受傷躺在床上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.42,0:08:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心哪有心情去約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.96,0:08:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到了嗎？醜女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.92,0:08:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊  我怎麼都沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.70,0:08:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真笨  真笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.54,0:08:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.14,0:08:27.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有位叫緋村拔刀齊的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.21,0:08:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他怎麼會知道劍心的綽號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.55,0:08:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.11,0:08:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是這裏的巡佐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫藤田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.42,0:08:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是從署長那兒聽到\N有關緋村的事情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.99,0:08:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是署長的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.86,0:08:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.93,0:08:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是我們接到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.77,0:08:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人要暗殺他的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.30,0:09:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起  我可以在這等一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.11,0:09:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心可能晚點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你不介意的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.81,0:09:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.26,0:09:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是有人要你來殺我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.00,0:09:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人是沒有緣由就殺人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先請你說個清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緣由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.77,0:09:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你別擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.87,0:09:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等你死後自然會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.24,0:09:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別以為這樣我就抓不到你\N在左邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.21,0:09:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看得見我就快來抓我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.05,0:09:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就不信你的速度會比我快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.99,0:09:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不想動得那麼快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.96,0:09:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.66,0:10:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快說  是誰讓你來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.94,0:10:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回答  你到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟齊藤又是什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.05,0:10:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起  是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.95,0:10:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是受人指使的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.95,0:10:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是齊藤那傢伙威協我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.79,0:10:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.76,0:10:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤那傢伙到底想做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.40,0:10:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你所說的話我全相信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.77,0:10:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從今以後就快改過自新吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.50,0:10:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到你這麼好騙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中計了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.18,0:10:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣子看你怎麼跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.88,0:10:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.95,0:10:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙手被反綁的滋味如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.95,0:10:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且完全動彈不得了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比速度 你比我快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比力氣 你就比不過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人想暗殺劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.31,0:11:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 也是那個人 把左之助打成重傷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.65,0:11:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果真如此的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.65,0:11:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那他們一定非常強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.35,0:11:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要特別小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.56,0:11:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道劍心現在怎樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.06,0:11:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心是個機靈的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.56,0:11:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不必替他擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.33,0:11:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,千萬不可隨便出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.07,0:11:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有巡佐在此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.47,0:11:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待在屋內比出去安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.15,0:12:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以為警官只帶西洋劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到還會帶武士刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.29,0:12:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西洋劍哪有武士刀好用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是經過特別允許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.93,0:12:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以佩帶日本刀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.92,0:12:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也算是厲害的高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.83,0:12:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死的有點可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.46,0:12:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就照約定\N告訴你殺你的原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和齊藤他們一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.90,0:12:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是被政客派來殺你的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.07,0:12:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我不該讓你知道原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.84,0:12:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在黑笠事件之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.07,0:12:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓政客他們知道了你的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.84,0:12:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是他們害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.91,0:13:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在幕府時代幹過的壞事 被你揭穿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.48,0:13:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些政客們全都是一些\N做過見不得人的事的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.92,0:13:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.43,0:13:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難怪有人說齊藤是新撰組內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.93,0:13:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺手的不二人選
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.90,0:13:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你是裝死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到這個時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有像你這樣的笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.97,0:13:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.01,0:13:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我摔死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.84,0:14:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.91,0:14:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好擔心你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.85,0:14:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以後盡量少出門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.72,0:14:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外頭有人想暗殺你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.56,0:14:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從哪聽來的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.36,0:14:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察署長派人來通知我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.96,0:14:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是一個叫藤田五郎的巡佐\N告訴我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.31,0:14:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對付赤末那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,花了你不少的力氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.35,0:14:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距離最後一次對決\N應該也有十年了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.59,0:14:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心 你認識藤田巡佐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.42,0:14:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你現在叫藤田五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.69,0:14:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用說的好短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.66,0:15:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用活的倒是好長的時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.43,0:15:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩 要腐化一個人也相當夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.87,0:15:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇藤陣也\N是你第一個殺掉的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你以前不是這種作風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.41,0:15:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去的你是個毫無缺點\N作風堅強的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.02,0:15:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要在決鬥時\N總是正大光明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.75,0:15:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正面迎敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.99,0:15:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會使用傷害敵手之親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓其動搖心志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.49,0:15:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玩弄小把戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還打算以之為人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.46,0:15:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等的卑劣手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已算不上是真正的武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.21,0:15:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只不過是新撰組\N第三隊隊長齊藤一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.01,0:15:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新撰組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.84,0:15:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來他就是.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要暗殺劍心的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到你不只武功退步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.34,0:16:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連頭腦都退化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我跟赤末那種人相提並論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.11,0:16:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們夠格嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.55,0:16:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早就知道他們是什麼東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.15,0:16:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們新撰組比誰都清楚\N你緋村拔刀齊的功力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.32,0:16:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是現在的你\N比赤末好得了多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.96,0:16:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為浪客讓你變得脆弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.73,0:16:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.03,0:16:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.54,0:16:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.04,0:16:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只想保護好我身邊的人就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已決定洗手不幹劍客了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.85,0:16:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼多強都沒有必要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.68,0:16:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.62,0:17:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的你沒有資格成為浪客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.32,0:17:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和赤末苦戰時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已來這很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.16,0:17:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自稱為警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.97,0:17:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的朋友們也都深信不疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.24,0:17:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我如果要殺他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.94,0:17:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨時都可以動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.18,0:17:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只這次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刃衛時也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觀柳時也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.25,0:17:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你眼前的一切\N隨時都會被奪走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.13,0:17:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電十太的一太刃的時候也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.16,0:17:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拱手讓人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.04,0:17:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人怎麼這麼清楚\N劍心過去的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.84,0:17:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個\N滿嘴仁義道德的偽君子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.48,0:18:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再說些虛偽的謊話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.95,0:18:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你胡說  只要劍心在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他一定會保護我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.95,0:18:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是有劍心在的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.22,0:18:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.76,0:18:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.20,0:18:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可以把他解決掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼好大驚小怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.88,0:18:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像你說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.78,0:18:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十年對我來說是很漫長的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.25,0:18:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但總比你沉淪於\N自以為是的正義中要好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.45,0:18:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武士如果不殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.16,0:18:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何能守護正義呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.76,0:18:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你難道忘了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.20,0:18:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.13,0:18:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,斬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我們聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.77,0:19:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人世間才有真正的正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.17,0:19:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對於目前的亂象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.81,0:19:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你難道還能視若無睹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.45,0:19:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.05,0:19:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都不會再殺人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.89,0:19:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.96,0:19:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛才說的都是白說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.97,0:19:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你想讓這姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.74,0:19:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死在我的牙突劍下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.19,0:19:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小薰  沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.43,0:19:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他要的只是我的命而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.30,0:19:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是無法避免的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.94,0:20:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.97,0:21:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飛天御劍流 龍槌閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心還是很厲害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.21,0:21:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你往哪逃 拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.91,0:21:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牙突劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.02,0:21:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心

